             was indicted for <rs id="t17831029-41-off221" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17831029-41-off221" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17831029-41-off221" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17831029-41-cd222" type="crimeDate">10th day of October</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17831029-41-off221 t17831029-41-cd222"></join>, one silk handkerchief, value 2 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17831029-41-victim686" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Smith
                  <interp inst="t17831029-41-victim686" type="surname" value="Smith"></interp>
